UC-UAW Bargaining – First Agreement 
Graduate Student Researchers (BR)  
UC Mini-Package G 
October 13, 2022 
UC MINI-PACKAGE G 
The elements of this proposal are offered as a mini-package, whereby acceptance of all  components is necessary for a tentative agreement on the package as a whole. Absent such  agreement, both Parties are allowed to revert to the status quo ante on all matters covered by  this proposal.  
• Appointments – Language to add this concept in the Appointment Letter: 
“Graduate Student Researchers who are disabled or become disabled should notify their supervisor or department to request reasonable accommodations, in  advance of their start date or any time during their appointment, in accordance  with Article __ - Reasonable Accommodation [link to article].”  
• Reasonable Accommodation – UC Proposal 3 – October 13, 2022 
• Joint Labor Management Committee – UC Proposal 2 – October 13, 2022